snippet.title: A Sneak Peek of Summoners War: Chronicles
snippet.description:
In Summoners War: Chronicles, we’ll make it through it TOGETHER. 
Take a glimpse into the dynamic storyline and unique powers of each character. Coming next year on iOS, Android and PC devices
